# Unicode.GeneralCategory.otherSymbol

**Case**

A symbol of another type.

## Declaration

```swift
case otherSymbol
```

## Discussion

This value corresponds to the category `Other_Symbol` (abbreviated `So`) in the [https://unicode.org/reports/tr44/#General_Category_Values].
